Video-on-demand and video broadcast operations carried out rapidly with the rapid development of the Ethernet, as well  video is very rich in resources, but now people’s viewing mode is also just stay the stage of the PC. This viewing habits model is not suitable for most people, most people still hope to be able to watch the video programming through the TV set, and there is an urgent need to develop a device to butt joint with TV set. To accomplish on-demand and watch online for network video files and solve this problem. A  network set-top box is designed through the methods of IP network in the paper, the resource of network video frequency can watch the using the terminal end of TV. The design achieves the desired results, and the research findings research up good prospects for the application.